```{r setup, include=FALSE}
library(here)
library(tidyverse)
library(dplyr)

getwd()
```

```{r}
fish_data <- read.csv("pisco_fish.csv")

fish_data %>%
  filter(campus=="UCSC") %>%
  group_by(year, month, classcode) %>%
  summarize(abundance = sum(count))
```

model: fish count ~ species ~ zone ~ year ~ month ~ site
